{"word":"G2004 - ἐπιτάσσω - epitássō - ep-ee-tas'-so - Charge","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιτάσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epitássō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-tas'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Charge</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கட்டளையிடு"},{"paragraph":"to enjoin upon, order, command, charge"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5021 - τάσσω - tássō - tas'-so/5021\">G5021</a>; to <i>arrange upon</i>, that is, <i>order:</i> - charge, command, injoin.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1296/1296\">G1296</a>, <a href=\"#/G1297/1297\">G1297</a>, <a href=\"#/G1299/1299\">G1299</a>, <a href=\"#/G2004/2004\">G2004</a>, <a href=\"#/G392/392\">G392</a>, <a href=\"#/G4367/4367\">G4367</a>, <a href=\"#/G5001/5001\">G5001</a>, <a href=\"#/G5021/5021\">G5021</a>, <a href=\"#/G506/506\">G506</a>, <a href=\"#/G5292/5292\">G5292</a>, <a href=\"#/G5293/5293\">G5293</a>, <a href=\"#/G657/657\">G657</a>, <a href=\"#/G812/812\">G812</a>, <a href=\"#/G813/813\">G813</a>, <a href=\"#/G814/814\">G814</a>"}]}